me.taylorkelly.mywarp.economy

Class SimpleEconomyManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.taylorkelly.mywarp.economy.SimpleEconomyManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EconomyManager

    public class SimpleEconomyManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements EconomyManager
    Manages the economy tasks.

    The SimpleEconomyManager operates on a FeeProvider that provides the actual fees and a EconomyService that provides a connection with the actual economy of the platform.
